                        <div class="display-unit">V (ë³¼íŠ¸)</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="calculation-steps">
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">ğŸ“ ê³„ì‚° ê³¼ì • (í•µì‹¬!)</h3>
                    
